## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- N/A for this initial phase, focusing on visual and functional correctness.

### Manual Verification
- Test entry of Long/Short trades with leverage.
- Verify P/L calculation logic against manual calculations.
- Test responsive layout on both desktop and mobile views.
- Ensure 'Psychology' and 'Mistakes' notes are correctly saved and displayed.
